"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qvi1665702713514.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qvi1665702713514.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qvi1665702713514.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qvi1665702713514\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Project\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__project_309465\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Project is a Main Development Object that defines the contents of an application or part of an application, and is used to control the build process. It is the starting point for all development and contains Reference Development Objects that refer to Main Development Objects.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__p_d94637e1_d94638e1_d94639e1\">From a Project, you can create new Main Development\n         Objects, define and generate deployable archive files. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"spu1692183913093.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/spu1692183913093.html\" title=\"A project is a collection of references to main development objects. It is used to create and organize components, modeled entities, and libraries that are needed to build the application.\">Projects</a>. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__topic_d63012e1_d63013e1_d63014e1_d63015e1_d63016e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673491e63\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__image_oxf_xys_4wb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/project.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">prj</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fct1665702713420.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fct1665702713420.html\" title=\"A Reference Development Object holds the URL of another development object and enables its parent object to access the information in the referenced object. It can be created, modified, and deleted without affecting the object that it references.\">Reference Development Object</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface archive files (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.uar</span>)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10466e1_d10467e1_d10468e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">prj:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProjectName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__topic_d63017e1_d63018e1_d63019e1_d63020e1_d63021e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673491e269\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__p_d94646e1_d94647e1_d94648e1\">Project specializes Main Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__li_d36902e1_d36903e1_d36904e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__p_d94649e1_d94650e1_d94651e1\">It can contain Reference Development\n                  Objects.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__li_d36905e1_d36906e1_d36907e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__p_d94652e1_d94653e1_d94654e1\">It does not have Code Containers.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__topic_d63022e1_d63023e1_d63024e1_d63025e1_d63026e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673491e293\"> Project Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__p_d94658e1_d94659e1_d94660e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__li_d36908e1_d36909e1_d36910e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__li_d36911e1_d36912e1_d36913e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__li_d36914e1_d36915e1_d36916e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__li_d36917e1_d36918e1_d36919e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__li_d36920e1_d36921e1_d36922e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Project Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Archive</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Name of the Uniface archive file. For example:\n                              <span class=\"ph filepath\">MyApp.uar</span>. </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Archive Readme</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Name of the Readme file to be included in the Uniface archive file. For\n                           example: <span class=\"ph filepath\">Readme.html</span>. </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Archive Version</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Release version of the archive file.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Connectivity Path</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">External Path</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Standard Path</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qvi1665702713514__table_d10469e1_d10470e1_d10471e1__entry__2\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Project Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Project A Project is a Main Development Object that defines the contents of an application or part of an application, and is used to control the build process. It is the starting point for all development and contains Reference Development Objects that refer to Main Development Objects. From a Project, you can create new Main Development Objects, define and generate deployable archive files. For more information, see Projects . Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: prj Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Reference Development Object , Property Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations — Compilation output Uniface archive files ( .uar ) URI format: prj: ProjectName Specialization Project specializes Main Development Object in the following ways: It can contain Reference Development Objects. It does not have Code Containers. Project Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Table 1. Project Properties Property Description Archive Name of the Uniface archive file. For example: MyApp.uar . Archive Readme Name of the Readme file to be included in the Uniface archive file. For example: Readme.html . Archive Version Release version of the archive file. Connectivity Path External Path Standard Path Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}